# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented here.

## Format

This changelog is the **master aggregation** file following the naming convention: `changelog.ddmmyyyy.<sequence>`

**Format:** `changelog.ddmmyyyy.<sequence>` where:
- `dd` = Day (01-31)
- `mm` = Month (01-12)
- `yyyy` = Year (2026)
- `<sequence>` = Sequential number (001, 002, etc.)

**Current file:** `docs/06-changelogs/changelog.01022026.001` (Created February 1, 2026)

### Versioning Rules
Follow [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/):
- **major** — Breaking API changes, major feature releases (X.0.0)
- **minor** — New features, backward compatible (0.X.0)
- **patch** — Bug fixes and small improvements (0.0.X)

**Version format:** `major.minor.patch` (e.g., `1.2.3`)

### Changelog Entry Format

Each PR creates a file in `docs/changelogs/ddmmyyyy.<sequence>`:

```markdown
## [Version] - YYYY-MM-DD

### Category (Added/Changed/Fixed/Removed/Deprecated)
- Description of change

### Version Bump
**Proposed:** major/minor/patch (X.Y.Z → X.Y.Z)
**Reason:** Brief explanation
```

### Entry Categories
- **Added** — New features
- **Changed** — Changes to existing functionality
- **Fixed** — Bug fixes
- **Removed** — Removed features
- **Deprecated** — Features marked for removal

